OL,3,CThe zero-carbon homes where energy
OL,4,Cbills are #100 a year
OL,6,FFrom the inside, the five properties
OL,7,Fthat make up the Hockerton Housing
OL,8,FProject look like millions of others
OL,9,Fup and down the country.
OL,11,FBedrooms, bathrooms and kitchens are
OL,12,Fdecorated and decked out according to
OL,13,Fthe personal tastes of the owners. A
OL,14,Frange of mod cons occupy corners and
OL,15,Fwork surfaces.
OL,17,FIt is only when you step outside that
OL,18,Fthe unique qualities of this housing
OL,19,Fdevelopment truly become clear.
