OL,3,CThe zero-carbon homes where energy
OL,4,Cbills are #100 a year
OL,6,FBuilt into the land near the town of
OL,7,FSouthwell, west of Newark, North
OL,8,FNottinghamshire, the bungalows are
OL,9,F"earth-sheltered". Standing on the
OL,10,Fgrass which covers the roofs, it is
OL,11,Feasy to forget that the homes are
OL,12,Fthere at all.
OL,14,FEach one is six metres deep, with a 19-
OL,15,Fmetre south-facing conservatory
OL,16,Frunning the full width of each
OL,17,Fdwelling.
