OL,3,CThe zero-carbon homes where energy
OL,4,Cbills are #100 a year
OL,6,F"If you can build homes like this that
OL,7,Fdon't require that much energy use and
OL,8,Freduce people's bills, that's huge."
OL,10,FThe surrounding 40,000 sq m site is
OL,11,Fused to grow crops, rear sheep and
OL,12,Fchickens and harvest water.
OL,14,FResidents pitch in to work on the
OL,15,Fland, run tours of the property and
OL,16,Fmanage events at an eco-venue.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
