OL,3,CThe zero-carbon homes where energy
OL,4,Cbills are #100 a year
OL,6,FMrs Yates said: "This is an example of
OL,7,Fhow everyone can live. With the
OL,8,Fclimate crisis and the national grid
OL,9,Fand going over to electricity, we have
OL,10,Fto look at how we fuel our homes."
OL,12,FJohn Grant, a lecturer in climate
OL,13,Fchange resistance, agrees. He says the
OL,14,Fproject is a model for sustainable
OL,15,Fhousing.
