OL,3,CThe zero-carbon homes where energy
OL,4,Cbills are #100 a year
OL,6,F"It's a better way of living that is
OL,7,Fnot expensive to deliver because of
OL,8,Fthe simplicity of the design and the
OL,9,Fconstruction meaning it can be
OL,10,Fdelivered at a comparable cost to new
OL,11,Fbuilds," he said.
OL,13,F"I am concerned that our new
OL,14,Fgovernment is fixated with building
OL,15,Fmillions of houses, which is great,
OL,16,Fbut I am worried that the regulations
OL,17,Fand the performance of those houses is
OL,18,Fgoing to be really standard."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
