OL,3,CThe zero-carbon homes where energy
OL,4,Cbills are #100 a year
OL,6,FHe added: "Unless things change
OL,7,Fsignificantly the world could be up to
OL,8,Fthree degrees warmer by the end of the
OL,9,Fcentury. So we will experience periods
OL,10,Fof very very cold and very hot.
OL,12,F"If we weren't to prepare for the
OL,13,Fchange, which is what the Hockerton
OL,14,FHousing Project allow us to do, that
OL,15,Fcould be catastrophic."
